    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Pro salute et Victoria et <lb n="2"/>reditu <expan><abbr>Imppp</abbr><ex>eratorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Caesss</abbr><ex>arum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Septimi Severi Pertina<lb break="no" n="4"/>cis et <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> Aureli Antonini <lb n="5"/>et <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ubli</ex></expan> Septimi <del rend="erasure">G[etae</del>] Piorum <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>Aug<am>g</am></abbr><ex>ustorum</ex></expan> et Iuliae Domnae <lb n="7"/>Augustae matris <expan><abbr>Aug<am>g</am></abbr><ex>ustorum</ex></expan> et <lb n="8"/><supplied reason="lost">ca</supplied>strorum <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Aiacius <lb n="9"/><supplied reason="lost">Mo</supplied>destus Crescentia<lb break="no" n="10"/><supplied reason="lost">nus</supplied> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>atus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>G</abbr><ex>ermaniae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uperioris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>num</abbr><ex>ini</ex></expan> d<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>evot</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Auf der corona eine Mondsichel. Auf der linken Nebenseite ein Blitzbündel, auf der rechten urceus und patera. Das Erhaltene war bei der Auffindung noch in einem Stück; inzwischen in zahlreiche Fragmente zerschlagen. Zahlreiche Ligaturen. (B): ILS: Z. 1: salute victoria; Z. 5: [e]t; [[Getae]]; Mattern: Z. 5: [[[Getae]]]; ILS: Z. 10: n[um(ini)?].</p>
            </div>
